2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>对<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision">动视暴雪</a>的收购已获得英国竞争与市场管理局（CMA）的批准——克服了收购的最后一个障碍。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl-preview-hands-on-3488629">《潜行者 2：切尔诺贝利之心》预览：残酷，但前景令人难以置信</a></strong></li></ul><p>在微软和动视暴雪宣布将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/call-of-duty-could-come-to-ubisoft-in-new-activision-microsoft-agreement-3486426">后者游戏的流媒体版权出售给育碧15年</a>之后，CMA暂时批准了此次收购。</p><p>然而，它表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsoft-gets-one-step-closer-to-buying-call-of-duty-developer-activision-blizzard-3502676">仍然存在“剩余问题”</a> ，需要通过进一步调查来解决。现在新的分析已经结束，预计收购将很快完成。 </p><figure id="attachment_3514574" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3514574" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3514574" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3514574" class="wp-caption-text">一个人在玩白色 Xbox 控制器 图片来源：Eugene Chystiakov，来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p> “今年 8 月，微软做出让步，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ubisoft">育碧</a>将取代微软购买动视的云游戏版权，”CMA 在<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/news/microsoft-concession-a-gamechanger-that-will-promote-competition#:~:text=This%20new%20deal%20will%20put,ways%20of%20accessing%20that%20content." target="_blank" rel="noopener">向媒体提供的一份声明</a>中解释道。</p><p> “这项新协议将把动视未来 15 年内制作的所有<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/pc">PC</a>和游戏机内容的云流媒体版权（欧洲经济区以外）交到一个强大且独立的竞争对手手中，该竞争对手雄心勃勃，计划提供新的访问方式内容。</p><p> “由于这一让步，竞争与市场管理局同意重新审视该交易，并于 8 月启动了新的调查。该调查已于今天完成，竞争与市场管理局批准了这一规模较小的交易。</p><p> “随着云游戏市场的腾飞，新协议将阻止微软锁定云游戏领域的竞争，从而为英国云游戏客户保留有竞争力的价格和服务。” </p><figure id="attachment_3514580" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3514580" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3514580" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/microsoft-activision-acquisition-approved-formally-by-CMA-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3514580" class="wp-caption-text"> Xbox Series X 游戏机 图片来源：Billy Freeman，来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p> “这将使育碧能够在任何商业模式下提供动视的内容，包括通过多游戏订阅服务，”它补充道。 “这还将有助于确保云游戏提供商能够使用非 Windows 操作系统来播放动视内容，从而降低成本并提高效率。”</p><p>微软副董事长兼总裁布拉德·史密斯（Brad Smith）对 CMA 终于批准此次收购表示感谢。他<a href="https://twitter.com/BradSmi/status/1712711053552107606" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在发给 X 的帖子中</a>表示：“我们现在已经跨越了最终的监管障碍，完成了此次收购，我们相信这将使全球玩家和游戏行业受益。”</p><p>收购完成后，微软将拥有动视出版、<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/blizzard-entertainment">暴雪娱乐</a>、King、美国职业棒球大联盟和动视暴雪工作室。其中包括<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/games/call-of-duty">《使命召唤》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/games/diablo">《暗黑破坏神》</a> 、《糖果粉碎传奇》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/games/world-of-warcraft">《魔兽世界》</a></em>等游戏的权利。</p><p>值得注意的是，这将在微软的保护伞下增加许多有影响力的游戏和系列，并在 2021 年获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/arkane">Arkane</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bethesda">Bethesda</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bethesda-softworks">Softworks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/id-software">id Software</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/machinegames">MachineGames</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/tango-gameworks">Tango Gameworks</a>等工作室。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，发行商 505 Games 分享了备受期待的赛博朋克动作游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/ghostrunner-2"><em>《Ghostrunner 2》</em></a>中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/exclusive-ghostrunner-2-reveals-first-track-from-returning-composer-daniel-deluxe-3513947">一首曲目</a>，该游戏由回归作曲家 Daniel Deluxe 制作。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsofts-acquisition-of-activision-blizzard-has-been-approved-by-all-regulators-3514539">微软收购动视暴雪已获得所有监管机构批准的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
